description: Inside God's Observatory Science Documentary hosted by Maggie Aderin-Pocock and Chris Lintott, published by BBC broadcasted as part of BBC The Sky at Night series in 2017 - English narration. http://docuwiki.net/images/d/d4/Inside-God-s-Observatory-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ This edition comes from the heart of one of the most influential - and surprising - organisations in the history of astronomy. Maggie and Chris have been granted rare access to the Vatican and its little-known observatory, the Specola Vaticana, perched on a hilltop 30km outside Rome.
